<SYNC Start=235466><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=235702><P Class=ENCC>
Yes! Yes, I did.<br>But what I didn't say....
<SYNC Start=238671><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=238938><P Class=ENCC>
