<SYNC Start=278909><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=280346><P Class=ENCC>
Awful play, man!
<SYNC Start=284214><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=284417><P Class=ENCC>
Her name's Aurora. She's ltalian<br>and she pronounces my name " Chandler. "
<SYNC Start=288911><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=290857><P Class=ENCC>
I like that better.
<SYNC Start=292188><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=292392><P Class=ENCC>
The usher gave me this.
<SYNC Start=294121><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=294427><P Class=ENCC>
-What is it?<br>-The Estelle Leonard T alent Agency.
<SYNC Start=297521><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=297730><P Class=ENCC>
An agency left its card.<br>They wanna sign me!
<SYNC Start=300460><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=300667><P Class=ENCC>
Based on this play?
<SYNC Start=302225><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=304337><P Class=ENCC>
Based on this play!
<SYNC Start=306430><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
