<SYNC Start=396763><P Class=ENCC>
Of course I wanna sign you!
<SYNC Start=398822><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=399599><P Class=ENCC>
-Miss Leonard, I'm so<br>-Oh, boy.
<SYNC Start=402033><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=402235><P Class=ENCC>
-Ride them, cowboy.<br>-l' m sorry!
<SYNC Start=405068><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=415181><P Class=ENCC>
I don't see it!
<SYNC Start=418309><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=419886><P Class=ENCC>
